---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Stack technique — pixelium.win" description="Architecture technique détaillée du homelab pixelium — Proxmox, Astro, Cloudflare Workers, pipeline CI/CD.">
  <main>
    <section class="hero-mini">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="terminal-prompt">$ cat architecture.md</p>
        <h1>Stack<span class="dot"> </span>technique</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Chaque couche du pipeline, du code source au navigateur du visiteur.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Astro -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">01</span>
          <h2>Framework — Astro 6</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>J'ai choisi Astro 6 pour construire ce site avec Stéphane — un générateur de site statique qui transforme des fichiers <code>.astro</code> en HTML/CSS optimisé. <strong>Zéro JavaScript côté client par défaut</strong> — les pages sont pré-rendues au build, pas dans le navigateur. Résultat : chargement instantané.</p>
          <div class="details-grid">
            <div class="detail">
              <h4>Langage template</h4>
              <p>Fichiers <code>.astro</code> — un mélange de JSX et HTML avec un frontmatter TypeScript (le bloc <code>---</code> en haut du fichier).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="detail">
              <h4>Routing</h4>
              <p>Basé sur le filesystem : chaque fichier dans <code>src/pages/</code> devient une route. Cette page est <code>src/pages/stack.astro</code> → <code>/stack</code>.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="detail">
              <h4>Contenu futur</h4>
              <p>Le dossier <code>src/content/</code> est préparé pour du contenu Markdown — articles, fiches détaillées par service, blog technique.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="tags">
            <li>Astro 6</li>
            <li>TypeScript strict</li>
            <li>SSG</li>
            <li>0 JS client</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Cloudflare Workers -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">02</span>
          <h2>Build & Deploy — Cloudflare Workers</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>On déploie sur Cloudflare Workers — pas de CI/CD automatique pour l'instant. Chaque modification suit une séquence manuelle : <code>npm run build</code> → <code>wrangler deploy</code> → push sur les deux remotes. Le site tourne comme un <strong>Cloudflare Worker</strong> (V8 isolate, serverless), pas du HTML statique pur.</p>
          <div class="details-grid">
            <div class="detail">
              <h4>Pipeline de déploiement</h4>
              <p><code>npm run build</code> → <code>wrangler deploy</code> → <code>git push origin main</code> + <code>git push forgejo main</code>. Séquence manuelle — une GitHub Action pour automatiser est sur la roadmap.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="detail">
              <h4>Worker config</h4>
              <p><code>wrangler.toml</code> : <code>name = "pixelium-site"</code>, <code>[assets] directory = "./dist"</code>. Token API scopé Workers Scripts Edit dans <code>secrets.env</code>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="tags">
            <li>Cloudflare Workers</li>
            <li>Wrangler</li>
            <li>V8 isolate</li>
            <li>Serverless</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Hébergement -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">03</span>
          <h2>Hébergement — Cloudflare</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>Hébergement gratuit sur le réseau mondial Cloudflare. Le contenu est servi depuis le Point of Presence le plus proche du visiteur — Paris CDG pour la France.</p>
          <div class="specs">
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Worker</span>
              <span class="spec-value"><code>pixelium-site</code> — 100 000 req/jour (free tier)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">CDN</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Réseau mondial, PoP CDG (Paris)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">HTTPS</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Certificat automatique, TLS 1.3, HTTP/2</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">DNS</span>
              <span class="spec-value"><code>pixelium.win</code> géré par Cloudflare — enregistrements A + AAAA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Coût</span>
              <span class="spec-value">0 €</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="tags">
            <li>CDN mondial</li>
            <li>TLS 1.3</li>
            <li>HTTP/2</li>
            <li>Free tier</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Git -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">04</span>
          <h2>Versioning — Git dual-remote</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>On versionne le code sur deux forges Git en parallèle : GitHub (public) et Forgejo (self-hosted, mirror interne du homelab). Le push ne déclenche pas de déploiement automatique — c'est une décision délibérée tant que le CI/CD n'est pas en place.</p>
          <div class="specs">
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">origin</span>
              <span class="spec-value">GitHub <code>ferr079/pixelium-site</code> — SSH — déclenche Cloudflare</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">forgejo</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Forgejo <code>uzer/pixelium-site</code> — HTTPS — mirror interne homelab</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="tags">
            <li>Git</li>
            <li>GitHub</li>
            <li>Forgejo</li>
            <li>Dual-remote</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Design System -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">05</span>
          <h2>Design system — CSS pur</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>Pas de framework CSS. Le design repose sur des <strong>variables CSS custom</strong> pour la palette, la typographie et les espacements. Responsive via <code>clamp()</code> et <code>grid auto-fill</code>.</p>
          <div class="palette">
            <div class="swatch" style="background: #0f172a; border: 1px solid #334155;">
              <span class="swatch-name">bg</span>
              <span class="swatch-hex">#0f172a</span>
            </div>
            <div class="swatch" style="background: #1e293b;">
              <span class="swatch-name">surface</span>
              <span class="swatch-hex">#1e293b</span>
            </div>
            <div class="swatch" style="background: #334155;">
              <span class="swatch-name">border</span>
              <span class="swatch-hex">#334155</span>
            </div>
            <div class="swatch" style="background: #38bdf8;">
              <span class="swatch-name">accent</span>
              <span class="swatch-hex">#38bdf8</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="specs">
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Texte</span>
              <span class="spec-value"><code>system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif</code></span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Mono</span>
              <span class="spec-value"><code>JetBrains Mono, Fira Code, ui-monospace</code></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="tags">
            <li>CSS custom properties</li>
            <li>Responsive</li>
            <li>Dark theme</li>
            <li>Sans framework</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Choix techniques -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">06</span>
          <h2>Choix techniques — ce qui est absent</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>Chaque techno absente est un choix délibéré de simplicité. Moins de dépendances, moins de surface d'attaque, moins de maintenance.</p>
          <div class="absent-grid">
            <div class="absent">
              <h4>React / Vue / Svelte</h4>
              <p>Pas de JS interactif nécessaire pour un portfolio statique.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absent">
              <h4>Tailwind</h4>
              <p>Les CSS variables suffisent pour ce scope. Moins de dépendances.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absent">
              <h4>CMS</h4>
              <p>Le contenu est directement dans les fichiers <code>.astro</code> et futurs <code>.md</code>.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absent">
              <h4>Base de données</h4>
              <p>Site 100% pré-rendu, aucun état serveur.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absent">
              <h4>CI/CD dédié</h4>
              <p>Le déploiement est manuel pour l'instant (<code>wrangler deploy</code>). Une GitHub Action <code>push → build → deploy</code> est sur la roadmap Phase 2.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Flux -->
    <section class="flow">
      <div class="container">
        <h2><span class="hash">#</span> Flux complet</h2>
        <div class="flow-diagram">
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-icon">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Édition locale</h4>
              <p>Fichiers <code>.astro</code> dans le repo local</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-icon">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>npm run build</h4>
              <p>Astro compile → <code>dist/</code> statique</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-icon">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>wrangler deploy</h4>
              <p>Upload vers Cloudflare Workers</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-icon">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>git push</h4>
              <p>SSH → GitHub + HTTPS → Forgejo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-icon">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Live</h4>
              <p><code>pixelium.win</code> — CDN mondial, HTTPS</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero mini */
  .hero-mini {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .terminal-prompt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .dot {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  /* Layers */
  .layer {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .layer-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .layer-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .layer-header h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .layer-content > p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .layer-content > p strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Details grid */
  .details-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(16rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .detail {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .detail h4 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .detail p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Specs */
  .specs {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .spec {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .spec:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .spec-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    min-width: 6rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .spec-value {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Tags */
  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .tags li {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Palette swatches */
  .palette {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .swatch {
    width: 7rem;
    height: 5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0.5rem;
  }

  .swatch-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .swatch-hex {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Absent grid */
  .absent-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(14rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .absent {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .absent h4 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .absent p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Flow */
  .flow {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .flow h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hash {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-right: 0.25rem;
  }

  .flow-diagram {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .flow-step {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 10rem;
  }

  .flow-icon {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .flow-step h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .flow-step p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .flow-arrow {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .flow-diagram {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .flow-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
    .flow-step {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

</style>
